#ifdef _MSC_VER
#define _CRT_SECURE_NO_WARNINGS
#endif
#include <cstdio>
int main()
{
	int t;
	scanf("%d", &t);
	while (t--)
	{
		int n, i;
		scanf("%d", &n);
		for (i = n > 45 ? n - 45 : 0; i < n; i++)
		{
			int foo = i, s = 0;
			while (foo)
			{
				s += foo % 10;
				foo /= 10;
			}
			if (i + s == n)
			{
				printf("%d\n", i);
				break;
			}
		}
		if (i == n)
			printf("NONE\n");
	}
}
